・・・

9.27 fri “Big adventure in a small screen”
.
小さな画面の中の大冒険
.
「ゼルダの伝説 夢をみる島」をテーマに作品を作らせていただきました。
久しぶりにこのゲームをプレイして、子供の頃にゲームボーイで夢中になっていたことを思い出しました。リンクが島を脱出するまで、私もゲームを抜け出せないことでしょう。
.
I now have created an installation about "The Legend of Zelda: Link’s Awakening". After a long time I played this title again and I remembered how much I was fascinated by Game Boy during my childhood. I’m convinced I won’t be able to quit the game until Link leaves the island.
.
───────────────
この作品の実物を、10月4日から10月6日までドイツのエアフルトで開催のMAG2019で展示します。
.
This work will be exhibited at MAG 2019 in Erfurt from 4th until the 6th of October.

☀️ "You are the light. Our light... that must shine upon Hyrule once again." ☀️ .

.
Sometimes I think about editing myself perfect - making my eye bags vanish, tucking away the hair poking out from my wigs. That's what I love about editing my own photos. I get to decide what I want people to see, and what I want to conceal. Lately, I've  been thinking a lot about the way attractiveness plays into your worth, whether that be measured by yourself or others. Everything online is fake, including this photo. Remember that. In the end, are you seeing people's hopes and dreams through a lense of their own creation, or a desperation to be a person they are not?
There's my late night deep thought for y'all.

***GOLDEN DEER SPOILERS IN THE SERIES OF PHOTOS!!!*** I just finished the Golden Deer route of Fire Emblem: Three Houses and it was a lot of fun. It gave more context to the mysterious group "Those Who Slither in the Dark" and their motivations. I really enjoyed this route and the characters. I do wish that it didn't share 95% of its battle maps with the Blue Lions path, but that's mostly a minor complaint. I still love this game. I just have two paths left to do, but those will likely happen in December when the third DLC wave releases. La venta de pokemons de 100% de IV es un tema un poco más complicado dado q es lento y no todos los pokemons están disponibles en todo momento. Dentro de este acto cabe una pequeña posibilidad de que el Pokémon salga shiny, como en la anterior ocasión esto aumenta el precio del Pokémon, para gusto del consumidor esto se preguntara antes de efectuar la caza, es decir, si tú quieres un magikarp 100 y no quieres pagar mas por uno shiny y te toca uno los quitaremos y buscaremos uno normal, sin ningún costó adicional.
La probabilidad de q sea shiny y 100% es muy baja pero no imposible si se nos da el tiempo suficiente.
El precio de un Pokémon con 100IV es de 40€ y el aumento por shiny de 20€ más 
Cabe decir q habrá descuentos para la gente q efectúe compras y descuentos aleatorios e incluso regalos en próximos sorteos .

From then to now!
.
.
That first photo popped up on my Facebook memories, that was on the final day of Acen 2012, I didn't even know what cosplay means til looked it up on google, this shot was from someone else, I've found this on google, for those who don't know, that was my very first con ive ever been to, I didnt fully dress up at that time cuz I don't have a budget for the overalls and everything, there were a lot of things I need to save up than just that, the rent is definitely one them, after I saw my first photo it made me wanna do a "then & now" post, Man I've came along way, now that I thought about it, I guess you should say that was my real debut of Casual Luigi was from 2012, not 2016, the 2 photos after the 1st one are the comparisons of my Regular Luigi cosplay, I wanted to match the real luigi but I don't have green sleeves at that time so I went with the shirt, but now that I finally purchased it, I won’t have to wear a green hoodie anymore, I could just wear that for my casual Luigi cosplay!
.
.
